that the mind that generates it thinks, whether voluntarily or involuntarily.\r\n\r\nIn addition to being able to produce phenomena known as paranormal and even extrasensory, as it dominates more about the physical world.\r\n\r\n<div class=\"callout alert\">\r\n<h2>E.E Meditacion Course</h2>\r\n<h4><a href=\"http://psychic-energy-healing.com/energy-enhancement-meditation-course/prana-meditation-course-super-chi-immortality/\">Level 0 - The Energy Enhancement Immortality Course</a></h4>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<h2>Psychic Energy Blockages and Meditation</h2>\r\n[embed]https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ZVxYSPezPeE[/embed]\r\n\r\nSwami <span class=\"original-content\">Satchidanand </span>explains how to remove energy blockages trough meditation. Physical body pain is the result of energy blockages, he also introduces us to the concept of karmic negative mass, using meditation for increment the levels of energy is possible dissolve those physical and emotional blockages.\r\n<h2>Energy Healing Techniques</h2>\r\nAs a result of a bad diet, negative emotions or stress, it is common the appearance of some energy unbalances in our physical body, that in time become in a disease.\r\n\r\nEnergetic therapy are based on the concept that the mind, body and spirit must work in a join way, in order to keep an equilibrium, and thus to work correctly and healthy.\r\n\r\nIt is necessary then, to restore the right frequency of a damage organ, so the energy can flow again, curing the organ.\r\n\r\nSome of the energy healing techniques are:\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Meditation</li>\r\n 	<li>Chromatic therapy</li>\r\n 	<li>Sound therapy</li>\r\n 	<li>Bach Flowers</li>\r\n 	<li>Crystals</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h2>Psychic Energy: Kundalini Energy</h2>\r\nThe arousing of Kundalini Energy which alone can supercharge the human bodies with Super Energy leading towards the removal of Energy Blockages and Illumination, EnLightenment requires the correct map.\r\n\r\nThe Kundalini Key of Energy Enhancement is described by a flow of energy down the front of the body - The Meridian of Chinese Acupuncture of the Central Meridian - down into the Chakra in the Center of the Earth outside of the body - \"Outside of the box\" called Kundalini Chakra from which all Kundalini Energy arises as if from a well.\r\n\r\nAs the negative energy is burnt up in the Fission Fires of the Nuclear Generator in the Center of the Earth which has kept this Earth Molten for Four Billion Years, a great tongue of flame arises from Kundalini Chakra up the spine  awakening Kundalini, purifying the Bodily Chakras and Ascends into the Chakras above the head for more Fusion Star Energy flowing down the front of the body.\r\n\r\nThe Energy of the Soul. The Energy of the Monad. The Energy of the Logos. the Energy of the Avatar of Synthesis. Perhaps access to Ascended masters and our past lives.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n[embed]https://youtu.be/a7UXavBz_rk[/embed]\r\n<h2>Energy blockages Effects on the Body</h2>\r\nThe negative emotional impacts, discussions, conflicts, dislikes, losses ..., are emotions that, if are not released in the moment, they become a very dense form of energy that obstructs the meridians of the body. These blockages have both physical and emotional effects.\r\n\r\nAt a physical level, these blockages affect the organs, they become inflamed and weaken and over time diseases are generated. Over time, these blocks begin to affect the emotional plane, producing anguish and sadness, which can lead to depression.\r\n\r\nThat is why it is fundamental to release these negative emections by means of breathing techniques and in a more effective way with meditation.\r\n<h2>Psychic Protection: Swami Satchidanad talking about The Power Towers</h2>\r\n[embed]https://youtu.be/OVV_kY9J1oo[/embed]\r\n\r\nHigh levels of Energy flows from above to below, looking for an equilibrium, but the negative energy also flows looking for an equilibrium, affecting everything around it, this is like a battle field.\r\n\r\nSwami Satchidanand present the Power Towers in The Psychic Protections, using external Antahkaranas between the Kundalini chakra in the center of the Earth and the Chakras above the head where all spiritual energy descends.','Psychic Energy Healing','','publish','closed','closed','','psychic-energy-healing','','','2019-03-23 01:18:12','2019-03-23 01:18:12','',0,'http://psychic-energy-healing.com/?page_id=15',0,'page','',0),(16,1,'2019-01-20 18:05:40','2019-01-20 18:05:40','','Home Page','','inherit','closed','closed','','15-revision-v1','','','2019-01-20 18:05:40','2019-01-20 18:05:40','',15,'http://psychic-energy-healing.com/15-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(18,1,'2019-01-20 18:11:04','2019-01-20 18:11:04','[et_pb_section admin_label=\"section\"]\n		[et_pb_row admin_label=\"row\"]\n			[et_pb_column type=\"4_4\"]\n				[et_pb_text admin_label=\"Text\"]\n					\n				[/et_pb_text]\n			[/et_pb_column]\n		[/et_pb_row]\n	[/et_pb_section]','Home Page','','inherit','closed','closed','','15-revision-v1','','','2019-01-20 18:11:04','2019-01-20 18:11:04','',15,'http://psychic-energy-healing.com/15-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(20,1,'2019-01-20 18:13:06','2019-01-20 18:13:06','','buda-head','','inherit','open','closed','','buda-head','','','2019-01-20 18:29:54','2019-01-20 18:29:54','',0,'http://psychic-energy-healing.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/buda-head.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(21,1,'2019-01-20 18:18:03','2019-01-20 18:18:03','[et_pb_section fb_built=\"1\" background_color=\"#fe0002\" _builder_version=\"3.16.1\" custom_padding=\"0|0px|0|0px|false|false\"][et_pb_row _builder_version=\"3.16.1\"][et_pb_column type=\"1_2\" _builder_version=\"3.16.1\" parallax=\"off\" parallax_method=\"on\"][et_pb_blurb image=\"http://psychic-energy-healing.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/buda-head.jpg\" _builder_version=\"3.16.1\"][/et_pb_blurb][/et_pb_column][et_pb_column type=\"1_2\" _builder_version=\"3.16.1\" parallax=\"off\" parallax_method=\"on\"][et_pb_text header_2_font_size